{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","settings":{"show_page_title":true,"heading_align":"text-center"}},"image_banner_azhThw":{"type":"image-banner","name":"Image banner","settings":{"image_desktop":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/BK_Pay_Banner.png","image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Finance.png","url":"","height_mode":"auto","fixed_height_desktop":500,"fixed_height_mobile":350,"overlay_position":"justify-center items-center","overlay_text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":false,"mobile_stacked":false,"color_scheme":"white","full_width":true,"transparent_content_color":"#ffffff","tint_color":"#ffffff","tint_opacity":0,"prevent_animation":false}},"multi_column_7kUh3i":{"type":"multi-column","blocks":{"column_CappyK":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1_03f3795a-73e4-4cf7-8d83-8d3d34c02a92.jpg","media_scale":100,"heading":"Pay later in 30 Days","text":"<p>Shop now <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/all-bed-frames\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/all-bed-frames\">bed frames<\/a> and enjoy up to <strong>30 days<\/strong> to pay after your purchase. <strong>No upfront payment, no interest<\/strong>. Simply buy at Bedroomking today and settle the payment later.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"column_CeatDJ":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_9df62df4-02b2-43c8-9a01-4d7758047853.jpg","media_scale":100,"heading":"Pay in 3 Months","text":"<p>With <strong>Pay Later in 3 interest-free instalments<\/strong>, you can split your purchase into three equal payments, making it easier to manage your budget. Your first payment is taken when your order is confirmed by <strong>Bedroomking<\/strong>, with the remaining two automatically collected from your debit or credit card after <strong>30 and 60 days<\/strong>. You can easily keep track of your payment schedule anytime through the <a href=\"https:\/\/apps.apple.com\/gb\/app\/klarna\/id1115120118\">Klarna app<\/a>.<br\/><\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["column_CappyK","column_CeatDJ"],"name":"Multi-column","settings":{"title":"Klarna's payment options","heading_align":"text-center","button_label":"","button_link":"","layout":"carousel","column_size":"large","column_align":"center","image_ratio":"1.77","color_scheme":"1","button_style":"btn btn--secondary"}},"media_with_text_D9kdgN":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_w6RJX7":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Who can apply for finance?","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}},"text_U4zXcC":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>To use <strong>Klarna<\/strong> when shopping with us, you’ll need to meet the following requirements:<\/p><ul><li>Be a UK resident<br\/><\/li><li>Be 18 years or older<br\/><\/li><li>Have a valid debit\/credit card or bank account<br\/><\/li><li>Be able to receive verification codes via text message<br\/><\/li><\/ul><p>Once you’re eligible, you can enjoy flexible payment options and bring home your dream bed frame.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_w6RJX7","text_U4zXcC"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitled_design_17.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":45,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"1"}},"custom_liquid_7PD4Kk":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"Custom HTML\/Liquid","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<div style=\"max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; padding: 20px;\">\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n    Sleep Easy with Our Interest-Free Finance Options\n  <\/h2>\n\n  <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555;\">\n    Make your dream bed more affordable. Enjoy <strong>0% interest finance<\/strong> and spread the cost in a way that suits you.  \n    Whether you’re upgrading your bedroom or investing in a new bed frame, you can pay monthly without paying extra.\n  <\/p>\n\n  <!-- Responsive table wrapper -->\n  <div style=\"overflow-x:auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; margin-top: 25px;\">\n    <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; min-width: 500px; text-align: center; font-size: 16px;\">\n      <thead>\n        <tr style=\"background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff;\">\n          <th style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; white-space: nowrap;\">Spend<\/th>\n          <th style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; white-space: nowrap;\">Interest-Free Period<\/th>\n          <th style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; white-space: nowrap;\">Monthly Payment From<\/th>\n          <th style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; white-space: nowrap;\">Total Amount Payable<\/th>\n          <th style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; white-space: nowrap;\">Interest Rate<\/th>\n        <\/tr>\n      <\/thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f7fa;\">\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">£600<\/td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">12 months<\/td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">£50<\/td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">£600<\/td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">0%<\/td>\n        <\/tr>\n        <tr style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">£2400<\/td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">24 months<\/td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">£100<\/td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">£2400<\/td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">0%<\/td>\n        <\/tr>\n      <\/tbody>\n    <\/table>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    Finance is available to permanent UK residents aged 18+, subject to status.  \n    Terms and conditions apply. Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.klarna.com\/uk\/terms-and-conditions\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #0074c2; text-decoration: none;\">Klarna.com\/uk\/terms-and-conditions<\/a>.\n  <\/p>\n<\/div>","section_height":"default","full_width":false,"dividers":"border-bottom","prevent_animation":false}},"multi_column_JNJmQb":{"type":"multi-column","blocks":{"column_mKtPJU":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_7071497f-6eaf-46d9-bf17-ca4236dab673.jpg","media_scale":100,"heading":"Interest Free Credit","text":"<p>Up to 12 Months - Enjoy interest-free credit for up to 12 months on purchases between £50 and £6,000.<\/p><p>Over 12 Months - For plans beyond 12 months, interest-free or interest-bearing credit may be available on purchases up to £12,500.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"column_XNFH83":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/4_57c67b97-a124-4def-8489-ffa5f82f5f06.jpg","media_scale":100,"heading":"Rapid Application","text":"<p>Get an instant credit decision in just 2 minutes and spread the cost of your order in a few simple steps.<br\/><br\/>Choose a payment plan that works for you, with flexible terms designed to suit your budget. <\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["column_mKtPJU","column_XNFH83"],"name":"Multi-column","settings":{"title":"DivideBuy's Payment Options","heading_align":"text-center","button_label":"","button_link":"","layout":"carousel","column_size":"large","column_align":"center","image_ratio":"1.77","color_scheme":"1","button_style":"btn btn--secondary"}},"media_with_text_6iUmUa":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_ne3c9p":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Who can apply for finance?","hea