.terms-link {\n      margin-top: 20px;\n      font-size: 0.95rem;\n      color: #00214d;\n    }\n\n    .terms-link a {\n      color: #00214d;\n      text-decoration: underline;\n    }\n\n    \/* Responsive Adjustments *\/\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n      .icon-row {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 20px;\n      }\n\n      .icon-box {\n        max-width: 100%;\n        padding: 20px 15px;\n      }\n\n      h2 {\n        font-size: 1.4rem;\n      }\n\n      .icon-box img {\n        width: 45px;\n      }\n\n      .icon-box p {\n        font-size: 0.95rem;\n      }\n\n      .terms-link {\n        font-size: 0.9rem;\n      }\n    }\n  <\/style>\n<\/head>\n<body>\n  <section class=\"dividebuy-section\">\n    <h2>Why use DivideBuy?<\/h2>\n    <div class=\"icon-row\">\n      <div class=\"icon-box\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com\/512\/10047\/10047452.png\" alt=\"Interest Free\">\n        <p><strong>0% APR<\/strong><\/p>\n        <p>Interest free instalments<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"icon-box\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com\/512\/753\/753318.png\" alt=\"Eligibility\">\n        <p><strong>No Credit Impact<\/strong><\/p>\n        <p>Check eligibility, no effect on credit score<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"icon-box\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com\/512\/1170\/1170627.png\" alt=\"Repayment\">\n        <p><strong>Automatic Payments<\/strong><\/p>\n        <p>Repayment automatic<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"icon-box\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com\/512\/1828\/1828640.png\" alt=\"Quick Easy\">\n        <p><strong>Quick & Easy<\/strong><\/p>\n        <p>Simple setup process<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <h2>Spread the Cost, Interest Free<\/h2>\n    <div class=\"icon-row\">\n      <div class=\"icon-box\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com\/512\/102\/102661.png\" alt=\"Add to basket\">\n        <p>Add items to your basket<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"icon-box\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com\/512\/906\/906343.png\" alt=\"Select DivideBuy\">\n        <p>Go to checkout and select DivideBuy<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"icon-box\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com\/512\/2920\/2920329.png\" alt=\"Credit Decision\">\n        <p>Provide personal details & get instant credit decision<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"icon-box\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com\/512\/1634\/1634233.png\" alt=\"First Installment\">\n        <p>Pay first instalment<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"icon-box\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com\/512\/638\/638528.png\" alt=\"Goods Delivery\">\n        <p>Your goods are on their way<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"terms-link\">\n      For more terms and conditions, please visit\n      <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/pages\/dividebuy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">this link<\/a>.\n    <\/div>\n  <\/section>\n<\/body>\n<\/html>","section_height":"default","full_width":false,"dividers":"border-bottom","prevent_animation":false}},"media_with_text_GXgfbx":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_gwrYLg":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Paypal","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}},"text_E4dPKx":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Get your bed and mattress with peace of mind thanks to PayPal Finance! Spread the cost by choosing PayPal’s finance option at checkout and enjoy flexible, secure payments. Terms and conditions apply. Find your perfect bed frame today and pay at your own pace.<\/p><p>Explore bed frames in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/3ft-single-beds\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/3ft-single-beds\"><strong>single<\/strong><\/a><strong>, <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/4ft-small-double\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/4ft-small-double\"><strong>small double<\/strong><\/a><strong>, <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/4ft6-double-beds\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/4ft6-double-beds\"><strong>double<\/strong><\/a><strong>, <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/5ft-king-size-beds\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/5ft-king-size-beds\"><strong>king size<\/strong><\/a><strong>, <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/6ft-super-king-size-beds\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/6ft-super-king-size-beds\"><strong>super king size<\/strong><\/a> at Bedroomking and get various finance options.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_gwrYLg","text_E4dPKx"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitled_design_22.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":40,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"media_with_text_DTKBtp":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_9Wixcz":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Clearpay","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}},"text_RQrtgf":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Clearpay lets you split the total cost of your order into 4 instalments, payable every two weeks. The exact amounts and payment dates will be shown for you to review and agree to before confirming your purchase.<\/p><p>If you’d like to make extra payments before they’re due, simply log into your Clearpay account and pay early - your remaining balance will be adjusted accordingly.<\/p><p>You can log in to your Clearpay account at any time to check your payment schedule or make an early payment ahead of the next due date. Shop our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/tall-headboard-bed-frames\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/tall-headboard-bed-frames\"><strong>tall headboard bed frames<\/strong><\/a> and split the total cost of your bed frame.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_9Wixcz","text_RQrtgf"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitled_design_20.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"right","image_fit":"contain","media_width":40,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"multi_column_J86QzL":{"type":"multi-column","blocks":{"column_MhpNBc":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5_162f7f1e-b0fd-4e35-ad2e-4db98c58841d.jpg","media_scale":100,"heading":"Pay it in 4 Instalments","text":"<p>Choose Clearpay at checkout and split your purchase into 4 interest-free instalments. Pay the first one today and the remaining three every two weeks, over 6 weeks.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"column_84RYJq":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitled_design_20_d0ed28d6-2b91-4fe9-9d7c-8ef1bc3d9d01.png","media_scale":100,"heading":"Shop Now Pay Later","text":"<p>You can log in to your Clearpay account at any time to check your payment schedule or make an early payment ahead of the next due date. Shop our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/tall-headboard-bed-frames\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/tall-headboard-bed-frames\"><strong>tall headboard bed frames<\/strong><\/a> and split the total cost of your bed frame.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["column_MhpNBc","column_84RYJq"],"name":"Multi-column","settings":{"title":"Clearpay's Payment Options","heading_align":"text-center","button_label":"","button_link":"","layout":"carousel","column_size":"large","column_align":"center","image_ratio":"1.77","color_scheme":"1","button_style":"btn btn--secondary"}},"custom_liquid_7hjhkD":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"Custom HTML\/Liquid","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" \/>\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" \/>\n  <title>How Clearpay Works<\/title>\n  <link href=\"https:\/\/fonts.googleapis.com\/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <style>\n    body {\n      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n      background-color: #f5f8fc;\n      color: #111;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    section {\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      padding: 60px 20px;\n    }\n\n    h1 {\n      text-align: center;\n      font-size: 2.3rem;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      margin-bottom: 40px;\n      color: #111;\n    }\n\n    .steps {\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n      gap: 40px;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      position: relative;\n    }\n\n    .step {\n      flex: 1 1 300px;\n      text-align: left;\n      padding: 20px;\n      position: relative;\n    }\n\n    \/* Dashed divider lines *\/\n    .step:not(:last-child)::after {\n      content: \"\";\n      position: absolute;\n      top: 0;\n      right: -20px;\n      width: 1px;\n      height: 100%;\n      border-right: 1px dashed #ccc;\n    }\n\n    .icon {\n      width: 60px;\n      height: 60px;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .step h2 {\n      font-size: 1.3rem;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      color: #000;\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .step p {\n      font-size: 1rem;\n      font-weight: 400;\n      color: #333;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n\n    \/* Mobile styles *\/\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n      .steps {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 30px;\n      }\n\n      .step {\n        text-align: center;\n        padding-bottom: 30px;\n      }\n\n      .step:not(:last-child)::after {\n        content: \"\";\n        position: absolute;\n        bottom: 0;\n        left: 50%;\n        transform: translateX(-50%);\n        width: 60%;\n        height: 1px;\n        border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;\n      }\n\n      .icon {\n        margin: 0 auto 15px;\n      }\n    }\n  <\/style>\n<\/head>\n<body>\n  <section>\n    <h1>How Clearpay Works<\/h1>\n\n    <div class=\"steps\">\n      <div class=\"step\">\n        <img class=\"icon\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0267\/6346\/0696\/files\/shopping-cart_1.png?v=1761141871\" alt=\"Bag icon\">\n        <h2>Get the app to sign up.<\/h2>\n        <p>No long applications. Have your email, phone number, address, DOB and debit\/credit card handy.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"step\">\n        <img class=\"icon\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0267\/6346\/0696\/files\/clock_1.png?v=1761141871\" alt=\"Calendar icon\">\n        <h2>Pay over six weeks.<\/h2>\n        <p>Choose Clearpay at checkout and pay in 4 interest-free instalments – make your first payment today and the rest over 6 weeks.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"step\">\n        <img class=\"icon\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0267\/6346\/0696\/files\/Untitled_design_1_8377ddf7-8666-4e64-94f7-4fce73dbad9b.png?v=1761142033\" alt=\"Piggy bank icon\">\n        <h2>Late fees apply if you miss a payment.<\/h2>\n        <p>No fees when you pay on time. We’ll send you reminders and cap late payments to help you get back on track.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/section>\n<\/body>\n<\/html>","section_height":"tight","full_width":false,"dividers":"none","prevent_animation":false}}},"order":["main","image_banner_azhThw","multi_column_7kUh3i","media_with_text_D9kdgN","custom_liquid_7PD4Kk","multi_column_JNJmQb","media_with_text_6iUmUa","custom_liquid_rMt3EN","media_with_text_GXgfbx","media_with_text_DTKBtp","multi_column_J86QzL","custom_liquid_7hjhkD"]}